LLVM examples with Sublime Text 3
---------------------------------

Install Sublime Text 3 via brew & cask:
  $ brew install caskroom/cask/brew-cask
  $ brew tap caskroom/versions
  $ brew cask install sublime-text3

Install the latest LLVM libraries, Clang and AddressSanitizer:
  $ brew install llvm --with-clang --with-asan --HEAD

Move the "LLVM Examples.sublime-build" file to:
  /Users/<user>/Library/Application Support/Sublime Text 3/Packages/User

Run Sublime Text 3
Load the HowToUseJIT.cpp from the examples folder 
From the toolbar select Tools > Build System > LLVM Examples
Build and run with Cmd+B / Cmd+Shift+B
